  "remarks": "\nJSC Zelenodolsk Shipyard is a Russian shipbuilding enterprise that has constructed more than 1500 sea- and river-going ships and vessels\n. JSC Zelenodolsk Shipyard is therefore carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia – the Russian construction sector and the Russian transport sector.  JSC Zelenodolsk Shipyard is thereby obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
